---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | Lighthouse Mentoring" 
  description="Privacy policy for Lighthouse Mentoring's wellbeing audit services. Learn how we protect your data and respect your privacy."
>
  <section class="hero-gradient py-20">
    <div class="container px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700">
          Your privacy is important to us
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-8">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-GB', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
        
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Lighthouse Mentoring ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our wellbeing audit services and visit our website.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3>Personal Information</h3>
        <p>We may collect personal information that you provide directly to us, such as:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name and job title</li>
          <li>Contact information (email address, phone number)</li>
          <li>Company name and address</li>
          <li>Information provided in surveys and assessments</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Anonymous Survey Data</h3>
        <p>
          When conducting wellbeing audits, we collect anonymous survey responses from employees. This data is aggregated and cannot be traced back to individual respondents.
        </p>

        <h3>Usage Data</h3>
        <p>
          We automatically collect certain information about your device and how you interact with our website, including IP addresses, browser type, and pages visited.
        </p>

        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide and improve our wellbeing audit services</li>
          <li>Analyze workplace wellbeing trends and patterns</li>
          <li>Communicate with you about our services</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
          <li>Protect against fraudulent or illegal activity</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Data Protection</h2>
        <p>
          We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. Our AI analysis systems process data in aggregate form only, ensuring individual privacy is maintained.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain personal information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required by law. Anonymous survey data may be retained for research and benchmarking purposes.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Sharing of Information</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share information with:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your employer (aggregated survey results only, never individual responses)</li>
          <li>Service providers who assist in our operations</li>
          <li>Legal authorities when required by law</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Rectify inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request erasure of your data</li>
          <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
          <li>Request data portability</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>8. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We use essential cookies to ensure our website functions properly. We also use analytics cookies (via Plausible Analytics) which are privacy-friendly and do not track individual users.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="pl-4">
          <strong>Lighthouse Mentoring</strong><br>
          Email: privacy@lighthousementoring.co.uk<br>
          <a href="/contact/" class="text-teal-700 hover:text-teal-800">Contact Form</a>
        </p>

        <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">
          Have Questions?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          We're committed to transparency about how we handle your data.
        </p>
        <Button href="/contact/" variant="primary">
          Contact Us
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>